    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>当坏人从未如此有趣！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >厌倦了当英雄、遵守规则和拯救世界吗？穿上你的白大褂，在 <strong>Mad Scientist Simulator: Society of World Destruction</strong> 中，从低级的“实验室小白鼠”一路晋升为终极的“辛迪加首领”！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款游戏中，你不仅是一个到处开枪的疯子，更是一位在实验室里精心钻研的邪恶天才。你的目标：完成协会的任务，发明新技术，并释放终极混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>核心特色：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/ae6048ec22f9a5d13957852450261f8b.poster.avif?t=1771883330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/ae6048ec22f9a5d13957852450261f8b.webm?t=1771883330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/ae6048ec22f9a5d13957852450261f8b.mp4?t=1771883330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧪 <strong>你的实验室与车间，你的堡垒：</strong> 混乱在街头爆发，但在实验室里酝酿。在化学和生物台上通过 2D 和 3D 迷你游戏制造致命病毒、酸性混合物和进行 DNA 改造。这还不够？<strong>前往车床，逐个零件组装你自己的定制武器，提升你的火力！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/1bdb946f81dc7390b53e72bfe4f8826a.poster.avif?t=1771883330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/1bdb946f81dc7390b53e72bfe4f8826a.webm?t=1771883330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/1bdb946f81dc7390b53e72bfe4f8826a.mp4?t=1771883330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🗺️ <strong>全球统治（作战室）：</strong> 不要把你的邪恶局限在街区，要把它传播到全世界！进入实验室的作战室，在交互式世界地图上选择目标国家，有策略地部署你制造的无人机和机器人，将城市逐一纳入协会的控制之下。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/f3a98ffa3cd13cd35a7b6a7a7d119609.poster.avif?t=1771883330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/f3a98ffa3cd13cd35a7b6a7a7d119609.webm?t=1771883330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/f3a98ffa3cd13cd35a7b6a7a7d119609.mp4?t=1771883330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚗 <strong>在城市中肆虐：</strong> 街道就是你的试验场！不要只是步行；偷走街上的汽车，让交通天翻地覆。用你压倒性的力量将无辜的人变成丧尸，或者用手感极佳的近战武器将周围的物体和敌人砸得粉碎。享受充满体素风格的搞笑战斗，看着手臂和脑袋在空中飞舞！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/d59b965ab9bf5f8999c8c10143fbded6.poster.avif?t=1771883330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/d59b965ab9bf5f8999c8c10143fbded6.webm?t=1771883330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/d59b965ab9bf5f8999c8c10143fbded6.mp4?t=1771883330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🚓 <strong>罪与罚以及疯狂的追逐：</strong> 小心，每个行动都有后果！在城市中过着自己生活的 NPC 可能会发现你并报警。随着你的通缉等级 (Wanted Level) 上升，你将卷入无情的汽车追逐，躲避巡逻车和步行的警察，奋起反击，或者甩掉尾巴逃回你的实验室。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/9d5bf93bd48ac7fda2a923e5f3dbff7b.poster.avif?t=1771883330\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/9d5bf93bd48ac7fda2a923e5f3dbff7b.webm?t=1771883330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4304890/extras/9d5bf93bd48ac7fda2a923e5f3dbff7b.mp4?t=1771883330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📦 <strong>管理与策略：</strong> 一个好的反派会很好地管理他们的资源。与你忠诚的机器人助手合作，整理你的物品栏，管理存储空间，并从黑市购买必要的补给品，为你的下一个大型“世界末日实验”做准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好了吗，博士？协会对你寄予厚望！</p>",
